sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HTTP as OVMS HTTP Server<br/>(Drogon)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as OVMS gRPC Server<br/>8443/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant MP as MediaPipe<br/>Graph Executor
    participant LLM as LLM Servable<br/>(ContinuousBatchingPipeline)
    participant MM as Model Manager
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant S3 as Cloud Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: REST Model Inference (via RHOAI Gateway)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OAuth/OIDC)
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    KRBAC->>HTTP: Forward (pod-local)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token verified
    HTTP->>MM: TFS predict handler
    MM->>OV: Inference request (in-process)
    OV-->>MM: Prediction result
    MM-->>HTTP: Inference response
    HTTP-->>KRBAC: JSON response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON prediction result

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: LLM Chat Completion (Streaming SSE)
    Client->>HTTP: POST /v3/{graph}/chat/completions<br/>Auth: API Key (optional Bearer)
    HTTP->>MP: Route to HttpLLMCalculator
    MP->>LLM: Chat completion request
    Note over LLM: Jinja2 template processing<br/>(pybind11 Python)
    LLM->>OV: ContinuousBatchingPipeline<br/>Token generation
    loop Streaming tokens
        OV-->>LLM: Generated token
        LLM-->>MP: Token chunk
        MP-->>HTTP: SSE event
        HTTP-->>Client: data: {"choices":[...]}\n\n<br/>text/event-stream
    end
    HTTP-->>Client: data: [DONE]\n\n

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: gRPC Model Inference (Direct)
    Client->>gRPC: ModelInfer RPC<br/>8443/TCP gRPC/HTTP2<br/>InsecureCredentials (no TLS)
    gRPC->>MM: KServe v2 inference
    MM->>OV: Model inference (in-process)
    OV-->>MM: Result tensors
    MM-->>gRPC: InferResponse
    gRPC-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Model Loading from Cloud Storage
    MM->>S3: List/Download model files<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / GCS SA / Azure
    S3-->>MM: Model artifacts
    Note over MM: Cache to local directory<br/>MD5 validation
    MM->>OV: ov::Core::compile_model()
    Note over OV: Model compiled and ready
